<h2 class="data-title">Sale Information</h2>
<span class="icon icon-tooltip selector" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" data-html="true" data-content="<div class='tooltip-w-md tooltip--sale-info text-md'><ul class='list-tooltip'><li><strong>Item #: </strong> A number an IAA branch assigns to each vehicle in a particular sale. This number is intended to make it easier to follow vehicles of interest in a specific sale.</li><ul class='mb-15'><li><strong>Sample: </strong> Item #: 10&rdquo;could reference a stock you are interested in at an auction this week. If this stock were to be re-run next week it might have &ldquo;Item #: 15&rdquo;assigned to it but the stock # would remain the same.<li><strong>Tip: </strong>Item #s are displayed 2 business days prior to an auction but can still change. We recommend reviewing the Item # the day of the auction.</ul><li><strong>Lane: </strong>Some of IAAs branches run 2 or more lanes for their sale. The first lane is referenced with an&ldquo;A&rdquo;.The second lane is referenced with a &ldquo;B&rdquo; and so forth.</li><ul><li><strong>Sample: </strong> If &ldquo;Item #:45&rdquo; is in the auctions second lane then you will see it referenced as &ldquo;Lane:B Item #: 45&rdquo; .<li><strong>Tip: </strong>Know the lanes of the vehicles you are interested in before bidding live online or live in person. It will enable you to select the correct auction lane when bidding online and, the correct auctioneer when attending the sale at the branch.</ul><li><b>Actual Cash Value:</b> The estimated retail price of the item in its pre-damage condition that the Seller has provided to IAA. This amount is not a guarantee of the value of the vehicle.<br/><li><b>Estimated Repair Cost:</b> The cost of repair that the Seller has provided to IAA, based on the Sellers research and calculations. The estimate is not a guarantee of total costs to repair the vehicle.<br/><li><b>Title/Sale Doc:</b> The ownership document that will be transferred to the buyer upon completion of sale. All sale documents are subject to state laws based on the state where they are issued. The sale document issued for any vehicle is the current ownership document for the vehicle and in no way does it represent or attempt to represent any prior title history of the vehicle.<br/><li><b>Title/Sale Doc Brand:</b> The type of title. Some examples are Duplicate or Parts Only. The brands and the criteria used to assign them vary widely from one state to another.<br/><li><b>Title/Sale Doc Notes:</b> Special notes provided by the IAA branch that handled the title/sale document. This section may indicate important information that can impact how the vehicle can be sold.<br/><li><strong>Stock #: </strong> A unique number IAA assigns to each vehicle. This 7-8 digit number can be used to identify a vehicle before, during and after the auction.</li><ul><li><strong>Tip: </strong> Enter the stock number in the sites keyword search box to quickly find the status of a vehicle.</ul></ul></div>">

$('body').tooltip({
selector: '[data-toggle="tooltip"]'
});
$(document).ready(function () {
$(window).on('load resize scroll', function () {

if ('True') {

if ($("#similarVehiclesContainer").isInViewport()) {
if ($("#IsSimilarVehiclesLoaded").val() == "false") {

if ($('#hdnRequestedItemID').val() != '') {

loadSimilarVehicles($('#hdnRequestedItemID').val(), "desktop", $('#hdnSimilarVehicleSelected').val());
}
}
$("#IsSimilarVehiclesLoaded").val("true");
}

$("#similarVehiclesContainer #retry").on("click", function (event) {
if ($('#hdnRequestedItemID').val() != '') {
loadSimilarVehicles($('#hdnRequestedItemID').val(), "desktop", $('#hdnSimilarVehicleSelected').val());
$("#IsSimilarVehiclesLoaded").val("true");
}
})
}
});
});
$.fn.isInViewport = function () {
var elementTop = $(this).offset().top;
var elementBottom = elementTop + $(this).outerHeight();
var viewportTop = $(window).scrollTop();
var viewportBottom = viewportTop + $(window).height();
return elementBottom > viewportTop && elementTop < viewportBottom;
};
function collapseAllTabs() {
$(".panel-collapse").collapse('hide');
}

function validate(evt) {
var theEvent = evt || window.event;

// Handle paste
if (theEvent.type === 'paste') {
key = event.clipboardData.getData('text/plain');
} else {
// Handle key press
var key = theEvent.keyCode || theEvent.which;
key = String.fromCharCode(key);
}
var regex = /[0-9]|\./;
if (!regex.test(key)) {
theEvent.returnValue = false;
if (theEvent.preventDefault) theEvent.preventDefault();
}
}
// Tooltip function to allow tooltip to stay open
var originalLeave = $.fn.tooltip.Constructor.prototype.leave;
$.fn.tooltip.Constructor.prototype.leave = function (obj) {
var self = obj instanceof this.constructor ?
obj : $(obj.currentTarget)[this.type](this.getDelegateOptions()).data('bs.' + this.type)
var container, timeout;

originalLeave.call(this, obj);

if (obj.currentTarget) {
container = $(obj.currentTarget).siblings('.tooltip')
timeout = self.timeout;
container.one('mouseenter', function () {
//We entered the actual popover call off the dogs
clearTimeout(timeout);
//Let's monitor popover content instead
container.one('mouseleave', function () {
$.fn.tooltip.Constructor.prototype.leave.call(self, self);
});
})
}
};
</script>

<script async>

var salvageId = 43822710;
var SignalRHubName = '/timedauctionhub';
var UserLoggedIn = 'True';
var UserSubjectId = '06843b5e-e329-4f2e-8390-7973911ba938';
var ItemID = '60605112';


function bindConnectionMessage(connection) {
var messageCallback = function (timedBidEvent) {
if (!timedBidEvent) return;

if (timedBidEvent.salvageId == salvageId.toString()) {
//Update the UI
$(".prebidCurrentHigh").text("$" + timedBidEvent.currentHighBid);
$('.startingBid').hide();
if (timedBidEvent.winninStatus.toLowerCase() == "winning" && timedBidEvent.winnerSubjectId == UserSubjectId) {
$("#timedbidstatus" + timedBidEvent.itemId).removeClass("text-color-error").addClass("text-color-success");
$("#timedbidstatus" + timedBidEvent.itemId).text("(Winning)");
}
else {
$("#timedbidstatus" + timedBidEvent.itemId).removeClass("text-color-success").addClass("text-color-error");
$("#timedbidstatus" + timedBidEvent.itemId).text("(Outbid)");
}

if (timedBidEvent.reserveMet) {
$("#dvtimedreserveprice_" + timedBidEvent.itemId).replaceWith("<div id='dvtimedreserveprice_" + timedBidEvent.itemId + "'><span class='badge badge-md badge-ol badge-success mb-15'>" + ReserveMetStatusText + "</span></div>");
}
else {
$("#dvtimedreserveprice_" + timedBidEvent.itemId).replaceWith("<div id='dvtimedreserveprice_" + timedBidEvent.itemId + "'><span class='badge badge-md badge-ol badge-error mb-15'>" + ReserveNotMetStatusText + "</span></div>");
}
}
};
var timedAuctionClosedEventCallBack = function (timedBidEvent) {
if (UserLoggedIn.toLowerCase() == 'true') {
if (!timedBidEvent) return;
console.log(timedBidEvent);
if (timedBidEvent.inventoryId.indexOf(salvageId) !== -1) {
$(('#prebid_' + ItemID.toString())).prop('hidden', true);
$(('#dvtimedreserveprice_' + ItemID.toString())).prop('hidden', true);
if (UserSubjectId == timedBidEvent.winnerId) {
if (timedBidEvent.status.toLowerCase() == "sold") {
$('#timedclosingstatus_won_' + salvageId.toString()).show();
}
else {
if (timedBidEvent.status.toLowerCase() == "buynowoffertowinner") {
$('#timedclosingstatus_buynow_offer_' + salvageId.toString()).show();
$('#btnBuyNow_' + ItemID.toString()).attr('value', $('#btnBuyNow_' + ItemID.toString()).attr("value").replace("$0", '$' + timedBidEvent.buyNowOfferAmount.toString()));
$('#btnBuyNow_Confirm_' + ItemID.toString()).attr('value', $('#btnBuyNow_Confirm_' + ItemID.toString()).attr("value").replace("$0", '$' + timedBidEvent.buyNowOfferAmount.toString()));
}
else if (timedBidEvent.status.toLowerCase() == "nosale") {
$('#timedclosingstatus_nosale_' + salvageId.toString()).show();
}
}
}
else {
$('#timedclosingstatus_nosale_' + salvageId.toString()).show();
}
}
}
};
//Create a function that the hub can call to broadcast messages.
connection.on('updateTimedBid', messageCallback);
connection.on('timedAuctionClosedEvent', timedAuctionClosedEventCallBack);
}
